## Rules & Patterns
- **Zero Backlog:** Every item in `product_requirements.md` must be marked DONE before the next sprint.
- **Directives Pipeline:** Owner can write tasks to `user_directives.md` at any time. These are NOT negotiable — PM auto-APPROVES them, Senior executes them FIRST (before R&D-generated tasks). After execution, Senior moves them to "Completed Directives".
- **Communication:** Analyst (06:00) -> R&D (07:00) -> PM (08:00) -> Senior (10:00) -> Developer -> Junior (Hourly).
- **Delivery:** Telegram notifications use `deliver: all` and the unified gateway session.
- **Verification:** Senior developer MUST verify code before marking tasks as complete.

